==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Loquat
<hw>Lo"quat</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Chinese name.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The fruit of the Japanese medlar (<spn>Photinia
Japonica</spn>). It is as large as a small plum, but grows in clusters,
and contains four or five large seeds. Also, the tree itself.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Loral</ent>⟦br⟧
